{"tid":418604,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇買UO嘅都入一入黎","createTime":"2017-09-29T16:39:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T17:22:02.000Z","uid":143499,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2ec76e249ec52ef631aafeaf85d62b5d677d481f","tid":418604,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:39:37.000Z","msg":"雖然貪平買HK EXPRESS嘅都抵撚死,自己亦曾經係大種乞衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但大種乞衣抵死還抵死，都唔可以畀呢班友仆街繼續偷呃拐騙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我在此呼籲大家好似對待何君妖一樣，報差館告佢詐騙。到時幾千個email差佬點都要有交代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nhong kong express就係搏你哋唔夠膽做， 即使唔關你事都唔可以畀呢班仆街好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9763e86709ce7e9d3d869b0e87db6b3b22f2ab6","tid":418604,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:41:50.000Z","msg":"雖然條款上寫明唔會賠而且佢有所有決定權，但係法律上都唔係完全講得通，曾經有案例講明呢啲條款係屬於不平等條款，喺法律上未必成立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以唔好畀佢條條款大到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d852365bcfca7118f758d9e9b80e1a9fa7f1973a","tid":418604,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:42:06.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"1d089d14033e1d22d9c95d5f47b94e4e8fff46eb","tid":418604,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:42:17.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"37005355c4c0a9368abb8fea73642d619389fe39","tid":418604,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:42:27.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"e9fc048360e2927fe95b5e32efc7714145ca38a4","tid":418604,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:42:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj