"msg":"咁唔一定個個都大種乞衣嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲人買個價都唔係平<br />\n亦有啲係因為就行程安排分開唔同機場出入<br />\n例如快運飛九州鹿兒島福岡就可以咁玩（如我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n不過只此一次<br />\n支資始終信唔過"},{"pid":"68554a457e112e44767e0ffcfa35d5d3dab69f8e","tid":418604,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:46:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3fc5605db076764c7570e17575157eeea8efd3d","tid":418604,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:48:37.000Z","msg":"邊個大種乞衣負皮我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ace9aee3bacb72aaa8e81eae09ca91312c2cc5","tid":418604,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:49:24.000Z","msg":"推上熱門大家一齊行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0603d46e8eb9f3fd67ea99304192fc924b695cc6","tid":418604,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:57:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d96bc577662b20b5631ae0d46e3eb998ac05c1","tid":418604,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:22:02.000Z","msg":"樓主冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}